"title": "2421: gospel, historical foundation of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "2421: gospel, historical foundation of",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The gospel rests upon the history of Jesus Christ: his birth, obedient life, atoning death, physical resurrection from the dead and his ascension into heaven.</p>\n<h2>The incarnation of Jesus Christ</h2>\n<h3>The historical facts</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:4-Luke2:7\">LUK 2:4–2:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke2:10-Luke2:12\">LUK 2:10–2:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt1:20-Matt1:21\">MAT 1:20–1:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:30-Luke1:35\">LUK 1:30–1:35</a></p>\n<h3>Its theological significance</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:14\">JHN 1:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:9\">JHN 1:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:3\">ROM 8:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor8:9\">2CO 8:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal4:4-Gal4:5\">GAL 4:4–4:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:6-Phil2:7\">PHP 2:6–2:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim3:16\">1TI 3:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb2:14\">HEB 2:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John1:1-1John1:2\">1JN 1:1–1:2</a></p>\n<h2>The sinless life of Jesus Christ</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:22\">1PE 2:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa53:9\">ISA 53:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor5:21\">2CO 5:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb4:15\">HEB 4:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb7:26-Heb7:28\">HEB 7:26–7:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:5\">1JN 3:5</a></p>\n<h2>The death of Jesus Christ</h2>\n<h3>An historical event</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:8\">PHP 2:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:50\">MAT 27:50</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark15:37\">MRK 15:37</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke23:46\">LUK 23:46</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:30\">JHN 19:30</a></p>\n<h3>Its redemptive significance</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:8-Rom5:11\">ROM 5:8–5:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:49-Luke12:50\">LUK 12:49–12:50</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:26\">LUK 24:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:4\">JHN 17:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:23\">ACT 2:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:19\">ROM 5:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:23-1Cor1:24\">1CO 1:23–1:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:24\">1PE 2:24</a></p>\n<h2>The resurrection of Jesus Christ</h2>\n<h3>Its historical reality</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:3-1Cor15:8\">1CO 15:3–15:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt28:1-Matt28:8\">MAT 28:1–28:8</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark16:1-Mark16:8\">MRK 16:1–16:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:1-Luke24:10\">LUK 24:1–24:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John20:1-John20:9\">JHN 20:1–20:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:8-2Tim2:10\">2TI 2:8–2:10</a></p>\n<h3>Its implication for believers</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:14\">1CO 15:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom4:25\">ROM 4:25</a> <em>in relation to justification</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom6:1-Rom6:14\">ROM 6:1–6:14</a> <em>in relation to sanctification</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:21\">1CO 15:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:42-1Cor15:49\">1CO 15:42–15:49</a> <em>in relation to the resurrection of believers</em></p>\n<h2>The ascension of Jesus Christ</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts1:9\">ACT 1:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark16:19\">MRK 16:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:50-Luke24:51\">LUK 24:50–24:51</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts1:1-Acts1:2\">ACT 1:1–1:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:33\">ACT 2:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:34\">ROM 8:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:1\">COL 3:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim3:16\">1TI 3:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb1:3\">HEB 1:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:2\">HEB 12:2</a></p>",
